doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    title About Us - CardioConnect
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='/stylesheets/navbar.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='/stylesheets/about.css')

  body
    include layout.jade

    //- Header with background
    header.header-bg
      h1 About Us
      p Connecting You to the Best Heart Surgeons and Hospitals At CardioConnect, we understand that navigating the healthcare system can be overwhelming, especially when it comes to critical health concerns like heart health. Our goal is to provide you with the resources and support you need to make informed decisions for yourself or your loved ones.
          

    //- Main content with grid layout
    .main-container
      .left-column
        section.about-intro
          h2 Welcome to CardioConnect
          p Our platform is dedicated to helping patients find the best heart surgeons and hospitals. We aim to provide clear, accurate, and up-to-date information to empower individuals in making informed healthcare decisions.
          p Whether you're looking for a top-rated heart surgeon or a hospital specializing in specific cardiac procedures, we're here to guide you every step of the way.

        section.mission
          h2 Our Mission
          p At CardioConnect, our mission is to bridge the gap between patients and cardiac specialists, offering trusted resources and tools to facilitate their journey towards better heart health.
          p Our platform offers a simple and effective way to find the right care and ensure quality healthcare for all cardiac patients.

      .right-column
        section.video
          h2 Watch Our Journey
          p Explore how CardioConnect has been helping patients across the globe.
          video(controls, width="100%", height="auto")
            source(src="/videos/VID2.mp4", type="video/mp4")
            | Your browser does not support the video tag.

    //- Full-width gallery with hover effect
    section.gallery
      h2 Our Partners and Top Certified Doctors
      .image-gallery
        img.gallery-image(src='/images/PART1.png', alt='Hospital 1')
        img.gallery-image(src='/images/PART3.jpeg', alt='Hospital 2')
        img.gallery-image(src='/images/DOC1.jpg', alt='Doctor 1')
        img.gallery-image(src='/images/DOC3.jpg', alt='Doctor 2')

    //- Footer
    footer.footer
      p Your journey to better heart health starts with the right information.
      p &copy; 2024 CardioConnect. All Rights Reserved.
